      <div id="mw-content-text" lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr"><p>There were two wars in the Transvaal (South Africa)  between the British and the Boers, of which the second is by far the better known. Historical accounts of the second war necessarily include some history of the first as background.
</p><p>Additional titles available via <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.gutenberg.org/ebooks/search/?query=South+African+War+!+bsxBoer">catalog search</a>.
</p>
